column2: SELECT CT.objID, CT.trainID, W.cntr AS wise_cntr, SQRT(SQUARE((W.ra-CT.raMean)*COS(CT.decMean*PI()/#))+SQUARE(W.dec-CT.decMean))*# AS match_dist INTO MyDB.Tmp_ClassTraining_NonSDSS_WISE FROM MyDB.Tmp_ClassTraining_NonSDSS_Objects AS CT INNER JOIN WISE_allsky AS W   ON SQRT(SQUARE((W.ra-CT.raMean)*COS(CT.decMean*PI()/#))+SQUARE(W.dec-CT.decMean))*#<#
